title: Episode 39 - CIA - Early Cold War
itunes:author: The History of the Cold War Podcast
itunes:summary: Join us as we explore the origins of the CIA and its influence on the early Cold War. How was the CIA different from MI6 or the KGB ? Learn how Washington Politics influenced the structure and growth of the CIA. Finally learn about the early clandestine missions of the CIA in the early years of the Cold War.
